text: Fanga () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltyayevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 4 km from Kaltyayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Fanga, Republic of Bashkortostan
